{"tid":1803291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國安全部門據報同意華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2019-12-30T06:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T06:02:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5134a245c8d3588e921a831e1e4e63d3065cff95","tid":1803291,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"在美國拉攏盟友封殺中國華為之際，英國傳媒報道，英國安全部門高層傳為首相約翰遜「開綠燈」，准許華為參與5G建設，惟初步建議將華為排除在「核心」範圍之外。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日郵報》引述消息報道，英國安全部門高層管理層有信心可平衡國家安全及經濟利益，允許華為提供5G手機網絡的天線等非核心配件。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜將於下月第三個星期主持國家安全委員會會議，拍板是否讓華為參與5G網絡建設。英國若允許華為參與5G建設，將標誌美國拉攏歐洲盟友圍堵華為再遇挫。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩此前警告英國，如果容許中國電訊設備製造商華為，參與當地5G網絡建設，將對英國情報機關構成威脅。華為則一直否認有關間諜的指控。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：林佩怡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2529762/【華為5G】開綠燈？%20英國安全部門據報同意華為參與5G建設\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2529762%2F%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA5G%E3%80%91%E9%96%8B%E7%B6%A0%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9F%2520%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%83%E8%88%875G%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=c416d9c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2529762/【華為5G】開綠燈？%20英國安全部門據報同意華為參與5G建設</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a2e3c470d939b2bc826e2824670a8f198c6eee","tid":1803291,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=01d18d5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"}]}